raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"orientation_hall\")
do unlock_gallery_image(\"jason\", \"1\")
Jason: Yo dude, was nice to meet you
Player: Hey!
Player: Likewise
Jason: What are you doing tonight btw?
Jason: Trying to get a bit of a group going
Jason: Since we're all new y'know
Player: Yeah that's smart
Jason: Hell ya dude
Jason: It increases our chances for a hookup if we're in a group
Jason: We can slide in if you catch my meaning
Player: I catch it
Player: But I'll have to see
Jason: What's there to see?
Jason: There aren't any classes yet so we won't have time like this until after sem
Player: I gotta check on my girlfriend
Player: Make sure she's settling in
Jason: Wow srsly?
Jason: Is she hot?
do social_post(\"mabel_orientation\")
- 😅
	Player: 😅
- Yep
	Player: Yep
	Jason: Wow shit, you're honest lol
	Jason: You gonna show off or what?
	- Nah dude 😅
		Player: Nah dude 😅
	- Sure thing
		set Story.flag = \"JasonKnowsMabel\"
		Player: Sure thing
		Player: img: mabel/1
		Jason: What an absolute BADDIE
		Jason: What's she like in bed bro
		Jason: Does she rock the crib or do you?
		- Actually, we never..
			Player: Actually, we never..
			Jason: Whaaat????
			Jason: Tellin' me she's a virgin or something?
			Jason: Someone's gonna hit that before you if you don't hurry up
			Player: 😆
		- That's a secret
			Player: That's a secret
Jason: I'm just busting your balls bro
Jason: That's fair though chief, you do that
Jason: I sent you my Social, for next time
set PhoneUnlocks.reveal = \"jason\"
Player: Yeah keep me in the loop
Jason: Will do
Jason: Peace
=> END"
